1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,000
在可观测宇宙的边缘，时间尚未成形，空间尚未绷紧……

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:26,000
一团古老分子云，在引力微扰下开始自我聚拢……

3
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:36,000
核心温度攀升，压力激增——一场沉默的点燃正在酝酿。

4
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:44,000
但这一次，它没有点燃——质量越过临界阈值，光压溃败……

5
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:57,000
物质向内归零，空间向外震颤——黑洞初生。

6
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:05,000
从此，那里再无光逃逸，只有时空本身，记下了这一道皱褶。

7
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:33,000
This is the final descent across the black hole's boundary—light dragged, time stretched, space itself beginning to rotate.

8
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:55,000
You are crossing the matter critical zone—every gram of gas frictioning, radiating, and annihilating at near-light speed.

9
00:01:55,000 --> 00:02:13,000
General relativity breaks down here… classical geometry dissolves, replaced only by the whisper of quantum fluctuations.

10
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:28,000
Scale collapses to zero—you’ve reached the smallest measurable unit of reality. Here, there is no 'position'—only the tide of probability.

11
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:45,000
Look—vacuum is not empty. It breathes. It sacrifices. And in doing so, radiates away this cosmic leviathan, slowly, silently.

12
00:02:45,000 --> 00:03:00,000
Each flash erases a fragment of mass—a moment of entropy reversed, a thread of spacetime memory quietly unraveling…

